-- China Construction Bank Says Central Huijin Will Buy Rights Offer Shares
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-21T22:39:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/china-construction-bank-says-central-huijin-will-buy-rights-offer-shares.html

          
          
             China Construction Bank Corp. said
Central Huijin Investment Co., the lender’s biggest shareholder,
will buy shares in the bank’s rights offer, according to a
filing Shanghai’s stock exchange.  
